        <div>
          <head rend="italic" xml:id="v2ch">An Attendant sings in a base.</head>
            <lg type="stanza">
            <l rend="indent2">Come heavy souls oppressed with the weight</l>
            <l rend="indent2">Of Crimes, or Pangs, or want of your delight,</l>
            <l rend="indent3">Come <seg xml:id="v3ch">down</seg> in <hi rend="italic" xml:id="v4ch">Lethe's,</hi> sleepy lake</l>
            <l rend="indent4">Whatever makes you ake.</l>
            <l rend="indent4">Drink <seg xml:id="v5ch">health</seg> from poyson'd bowles</l>
            <l>Breathe out your cares together with your souls.</l>
            <l rend="indent5">Cool Death's a salve</l>
            <l rend="indent5"><seg xml:id="v6ch">Which</seg> all may have</l>
            <l rend="indent2">There's no distinction in the grave;</l>
            <l rend="indent1" xml:id="v7ch">Lay down your loads before deaths iron dore,</l>
            <l>Sigh, and sigh out, groan once, and groan no more.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
